2026: Blissville Terraces - From Blueprints to Reality

  
  

Happy New Year and Welcome to 2026!

  

It is one thing to see a master plan on paper, but it is another to see it physically taking shape. As we enter 2026, Blissville Terraces located within the serene Caribbean Lake City Estate at Sangotedo is officially transitioning from a vision into a reality you can walk through.

The real magic, however, is what is happening just outside our gates. The rapid progress of the Coastal Road and the new Lekki-Epe International Airport is turning this entire corridor into the new center of Lagos. With the "Blue Economy" now offering faster water travel and the Ajah road expansion finishing this July, the lifestyle here is becoming as seamless as it is prestigious.

  

For you, this means two things: a commute that no longer drains your energy, and a property value that is poised to jump the moment those roads are fully linked.
